text: Jorge Jaime Schaulsohn Brodsky (born 22 December 1952) is a politician who was President of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile and as a member of the Chamber of Deputies, representing the former District 22 of Santiago. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:People from Santiago Category:Presidents of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile Category:University of Chile alumni
title: Jorge Schaulsohn
